text: [The shoot was conducted following strict COVID-19 prevention measures]
Today, I've come to Yeonhui-dong
for a shooting
And I'm planning on challenging myself with something new today
I think it's been a while since I've walked around like this
I'm going to buy some  yummy bread and try it out
[Yeonhui-dong Breadgrimage] [START!]
[forFour Bread] [18, Jeungga-ro, Seodaemun-gu] [Vegan bakery]
I've come to buy some bread
There's a lot of bread
There are a lot more types than I expected
What's the most famous one?
This one?
[Staff] The one on the right
This one!
I think I'm gonna like this one
Today I'll buy one for JISOO
and one that I'll have for myself
The bread is huge
This is something I could have for three meals
[Bought bread I could even eat for three meals!]
(Loves saying greetings)
[122m until the next bakery]
I'm walking around with bread and I'm feeling embarrassed
[Embarrassed but can't say no to bread]
I've arrived at the second bakery
I'll try picking out some yummy bread this time too
[Peterpan 1978] [10, Jeungga-ro, Seodaemun-gu] [Baby bottom bread, Shioh bread recommended]
I wish everyone could smell the bread right now
The bread smells amazing
I wonder which one is shioh bread
To be honest, I don't really know bread that well
So I'll show how a non-bread professional picks out her bread
(Deep thoughts)
This chocolate Shioh bread is for JISOO
I actually like Streusel bread the most
(Can see her contemplating)
I'll try buying  two baby bottom breads
The name is so cute, baby bottom!
This is really cute too
Roundy round potato bread
[Being impressed every step]
I have to have this
(How can you resist)
That's all
I'm such a huge fan
Thank you
It was one of my wishes
to walk around Yeonhui-dong to look around bakeries
and to eat yummy bread
[About to arrive at the 3rd place]
We've arrived at the 3rd place
[LE SOLEIL] [7-29, Yeonhuimat-ro, Seodaemun-gu] [Known for their Madeleine]
It smells so good
I'm really curious about this one
I'll get the nuroong
and rose and rich
I can't eat all this,  what should I do?
I'm thinking of going to the company
and look for dancers
and give them a bite each
[I thought it would go smoothly...] I just thought of a content
I'll try casting someone
I'm going straight to casting
[1st attempt full of confidence]
Will someone answer my call?
Unnie, have you just woken up?
[Casting a bread mate]
- At what time? - Before around 3?
- Before 3? - Yeah what time do you get in?
[1st attempt fails]
[2nd attempt with some doubts]
Where are you?
I've come out for a shooting
You're not gonna come to the company?
Probably not
(Embarrassed)
[About to eat alone] Oh no what should I do?
Of course I thought people would be at the company
They've all gone to shoot 'Street Woman Fighter'
I'm a fan of SWF too, should I sneak into their shooting site
Anyone who likes bread
give me a call please!
[3rd attempt,  almost begging at this point]
Sunho who's known for appearing on [Omniscient Interfering View]
What are you doing?
I'm going to the bank right now
Do you have plans to come into the company today?
I'm going straight back, I'm at the company today
Really? I'll come see you then
Alright I'll see you soon
I feel more relaxed now
[But couldn't meet him because of bad timing]
[I left it on his desk and he sent me a proof-pic saying it was yummy]
(Thinking hard)
[4th attempt with almost no hope] I'll ask if they can have bread
[Exciting ringing bell sound, quite opposite to how I'm feeling]
(Nervous)
[The person you have dialed can not answer your phone right...]
(Destined to eat alone)
[And just like that  I arrived at the company all lonely]
To give you a quick introduction
This is the new YG building
This is the practice room where we practice for our concerts
It looks familiar right?
It feels awkward coming in when there's nobody around
This place seems huge
There's a famous rice noodle place here
If you look here, there's an escalator too
[Taking a seat to eat]
Guys I have a lot of bread here
I'm going to put  a  post-it note and give it out
I've got 5 breads to try out
Where did my baby bottom bread go?
Oh it's right here
This is the baby bottom bread I bought from the Peterpan Bakery
I think they named it after the shape
The taste of this outside is really unique
I feel like I'm touching a baby's bottom
It's a taste I really like
I'll try tearing this bread apart
How do I eat you?
What should I do if the bread is bigger than my hands?
It's like this inside
They say you have to share yummy things with people
I like figs a lot
It's yummy
Next up, I'll try having some potato bread
It smells like  mixed grain powder
Why does potato bread smell like mixed grain powder?
Will it taste like potatoes?
It does taste like potato
It feels like they had bread dough
and slightly sprinkled  mixed grain powder on top
I recommend this  to those who like potatoes
[Next up is Madeleine]
This seems so yummy
Wow, it smells so nice
I'll try the noroong Madeleine
It's yummy, it's really nutty
They said they put cream cheese on top
I want to recommend this flavor
Since I've tried out these yummy breads
I'll walk around the company and give these to people
I'll leave the bread here putting my gratitude into it
I'll leave some bread like a bread-fairy
Chocolate bread that LISA likes
Everyone said they were coming in later
I said 'P.S. the chocolate one is for LISA'
I'm sure everyone will enjoy it
(Proud)
Today I went around to buy some bread
and went through many difficulties
But instead, I gifted them to many people with a loving heart
I hope they all enjoy it and leave a review on how it was on social media
It's been a while since I did a shooting outside
so it felt nice to get some fresh air
My challenge to become a YouTuber will continue on!
Bye!
Thanks for watching today guys!
I'll make dumplings with a dumpling
